high_descs: Move to the sink ahead of you
Pick up a knife from the sink

Move to the left side of the sink ahead of you
Put the plate in the sink

Pick up the knife that is on the counter in front of the sink.
Open the cabinet that is under the right side of the sink, put the knife in the pan that is in the cabinet.
Take the pan out of the cabinet, close the cabinet.
Go to the left and go to the left side of the sink.
Put the pan in to the left side of the sink.

high_descs: Look down at the yellow handled knife in front of you.
Pick up the knife that is in front of you.
Place the knife in the pan that is located in the cabinet under the right sink basin.
Pick up the pan with the knife still in it.
Move to your left to stand in front of the left sink basin.
Place the pan and knife in the sink.
